	(text "TP_PB8 - BOOT0 / FDCAN1_RX\nPB8 is shared between BOOT0 and FDCAN1_RX.\nOption byte nBOOT_SEL = 1 is set during production programming to free PB8 for CAN use.\nTest pad retained for CAN signal probing and emergency bootloader recovery\nProduction: nBOOT_SEL = 1, nBOOT0 = 1 must be written at first flash."
